    {
      "number": 2,
      "title": "不管...都/也... — No matter...",
      "explanation": "不管...都/也... means 'no matter... (the result is always the same)'. Formula: 不管 + [condition], 都/也 + [result]. It expresses that the result does not change regardless of the condition. For example: 不管下不下雨，我都要去。(No matter whether it rains or not, I'm going.)",
      "examples": [
        {
          "chinese": "不管看多少次，我都觉得很有意思。",
          "pinyin": "Bù guǎn kàn duō shǎo cì, wǒ dōu jué de hěn yǒu yì si.",
          "english": "No matter how many times I watch it, I always find it interesting."
        },
        {
          "chinese": "不管多贵，他都要买那张票。",
          "pinyin": "Bù guǎn duō guì, tā dōu yào mǎi nà zhāng piào.",
          "english": "No matter how expensive, he wants to buy that ticket."
        }
      ],
