    {
      "number": 3,
      "title": "动量补语「次」— Frequency Complement ci",
      "explanation": "次 (cì) is a measure word for frequency, meaning 'time(s)' or 'occurrence(s)'. It is placed after a verb to indicate how many times an action has been done. Formula: Verb + 了/过 + Number + 次. For example: 我看了三次。(I watched it three times.) 我看过一次。(I have watched it once.)",
      "examples": [
        {
          "chinese": "我以前看过这部电影，看了两次。",
          "pinyin": "Wǒ yǐ qián kàn guò zhè bù diàn yǐng, kàn le liǎng cì.",
          "english": "I have seen this movie before; I watched it twice."
        },
        {
          "chinese": "他去过中国三次了。",
          "pinyin": "Tā qù guò zhōng guó sān cì le.",
          "english": "He has been to China three times."
        }
      ],
