          "role": "同学",
          "gender": "male"
        },
        "B": {
          "name": "小红",
          "role": "同学",
          "gender": "female"
        }
      },
      "lines": [
        {
          "speaker": "A",
          "chinese": "小红，你看过那部电影吗？",
          "pinyin": "Xiǎo Hóng, nǐ kàn guò nà bù diàn yǐng ma?",
          "english": "Xiao Hong, have you seen that movie?"
        },
        {
          "speaker": "B",
          "chinese": "看过！我以前看过两次，非常好看！",
          "pinyin": "Kàn guò! Wǒ yǐ qián kàn guò liǎng cì, fēi cháng hǎo kàn!",
          "english": "I have! I've seen it twice before; it's extremely good!"
        },
        {
          "speaker": "A",
          "chinese": "真的吗？你觉得最有意思的是哪里？",
          "pinyin": "Zhēn de ma? Nǐ jué de zuì yǒu yì si de shì nǎ lǐ?",
          "english": "Really? What part do you think is most interesting?"
        },
        {
          "speaker": "B",
          "chinese": "不管看多少次，我都觉得结局最有意思。",
          "pinyin": "Bù guǎn kàn duō shǎo cì, wǒ dōu jué de jié jú zuì yǒu yì si.",
          "english": "No matter how many times I watch it, I always find the ending most interesting."
        },
        {
          "speaker": "A",
          "chinese": "我已经买票了，今晚去看，你去不去？",
          "pinyin": "Wǒ yǐ jīng mǎi piào le, jīn wǎn qù kàn, nǐ qù bù qù?",
          "english": "I've already bought a ticket to see it tonight. Are you coming?"
        },
        {
          "speaker": "B",
          "chinese": "去！虽然我看过了，但是我想再看一次！",
          "pinyin": "Qù! Suī rán wǒ kàn guò le, dàn shì wǒ xiǎng zài kàn yī cì!",
          "english": "I'll go! Even though I've seen it, I want to watch it one more time!"
        }
      ]
    },
